OL,5,G0200 Trucking Hell
OL,6,     FAlpha Recovery send a crew to a
OL,7,     Fchallenging, energy-sapping
OL,8,     Frecovery: a fuel tanker has rolled
OL,9,     Fdown a steep, muddy hill and
OL,10,     Flanded on its side. A huge digger
OL,11,     Fis needed to flip it over.
OL,12,G0300 Trucking Hell
OL,13,     FIn Buckinghamshire, recovery op
OL,14,     FSteve must deal with a
OL,15,     Fmattress-stuffed lorry which has
OL,16,     Fhit a low bridge. Rookie Paul
OL,17,     Ftries to extract a wrecked car in
OL,18,     Frural Derbyshire.
